{"tid":447790,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一齊喊？","createTime":"2017-10-25T15:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T07:52:24.000Z","uid":89362,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b97ff9117f3c7e79746ed0722e2aec38cb6f9671","tid":447790,"uid":89362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"好辛苦<br />\n掛住一個人好辛苦<br />\n望住一個鍾意既人唔開心好辛苦<br />\n見住一個好愛既人係咁頹住但又幫唔到佢好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n好心痛<br />\n掛住一個人好心痛<br />\n望住一個鍾意既人唔開心好心痛<br />\n見住一個好愛既人係咁頹住但又幫唔到佢好心痛<br />\n<br />\n我做到d咩？咪喊囉<br />\n我做到d咩？係咁喊囉<br />\n我做到d咩？繼續喊囉<br />\n我做到d咩？乜撚嘢都做唔到呀！<br />\n<br />\n其實我好想你開心<br />\n其實我好想你快樂<br />\n<br />\n其實我期待著<br />\n其實我等待著<br />\n其實我憧憬著<br />\n<br />\n多謝你帶我去你個世界<br />\n多謝你帶我踏上奇妙旅程<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講<br />\n我永遠都會係到。"},{"pid":"ff3079b172dace72405fbaf13705bc30302a8297","tid":447790,"uid":41005,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"女朋友唔係我身邊 <br />\n<br />\n佢份功課無左 佢喊 好想幫佢但幫唔到 都復原唔到 <br />\n<br />\n好心痛 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e76fe76d4547540c1af6abfc09de6568169f94","tid":447790,"uid":41005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友唔係我身邊 <br />\n<br />\n佢份功課無左 佢喊 好想幫佢但幫唔到 都復原唔到 <br />\n<br />\n好心痛 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢已經捱左好多晚夜 唔好再崩潰佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbee9e499d41fc66a61f86c113633da6a27ea919","tid":447790,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"好肉酸。。。<img src=\"http://www.msgweb.nl/emoti